title: Nike Tech Fleece: Inside the Innovation
description: The modern interpretation of fleece, Nike Tech Fleece is a unique thermal fabrication that merges a smooth jersey with a synthetic spacer to create warmth without weight. When applied to new and iconic Nike sportswear styles, the result is a fresh, shaped fit that's made to move.
